                <li>Independence, dynamism</li>
                <li>Listening skills</li>
                <li>Communication skills</li>
                <li>Organizational skills</li>
              </ul>
            </section>
          
            <section>
              <h2>Interests:</h2>
              <ul>
                <li>Sports – Football, Basketball</li>
                <li>Passion – The World of Information Technology</li>
